metadata.name: AMNESIA STATE • and • MUTANT ADOPTION #1/26
metadata.description:
As in my "EMP - LAB" series on VerticalCryptoArt, in this piece, I also deal with AI as a large collection of laboratories and ateliers, where things are busy and heated while practicing and trying out and tinkering.


there are no limits,
exuberant is great standard,
opening up new thinking and seeing spaces is elementary and evolutionary.


philosophical and psychological.
haptic and imagined.
always in the tradition of.: EXPLORERS
----------
***Created for [The NFT Magazine](https://www.thenftmag.io/readersgallery/) Readers Gallery***
